'''D.H.A. Football Stadium<ref>[http://karachiunitedfc.com/dirkufc.htm Karachi United FC directions] Retrieved 28 September 2010.</ref>''' (also known as Rahat Stadium) is a [[association football|football]] stadium in the [[Defence Housing Authority, Karachi|DHA]] neighborhood of [[Karachi]].
