'''Valdumar Augusto Té''' (born 14 August 1997) is a Guinea-Bissauan professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays for [[Vitória F.C.|Vitória Setúbal]] as a [[Forward (association football)|forward]].

==Club career==
On 22 September 2018, Té made his professional debut with [[Vitória F.C.|Vitória Setúbal]] in a [[2018–19 Primeira Liga]] match against 
[[FC Porto]].<ref>{{cite news | date=2018-09-22 | title=Vitória Setúbal 0-2 FC Porto| url=https://www.foradejogo.net/match.php?match=201915400010503| publisher=ForaDeJogo| accessdate=2018-11-24}}</ref>

